divs: Sighting DetailsTwo nights in a row. The same object that ive seen on several ocations. again traveling from west to east and again for the second time in 2 nights traveled over DIA Airport in Denver. The object looks like jupiter in shape and brightness and moves very slowly in a strait line. (seams to zig zag slightly, but could be an optical allusion). I checked J Track and found no satalites or HST at that time. I am wondering if J Track is showing real time, or something els. But after checking many posabilities of satalite movement I still didnt find any thing with the same trajectory as the object that I saw. Is any one els seeing this object.
Summary: Bright object moving slowly from west to east, unknown altitude.
